<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>liweitan2014</id><title>利维坦</title><updated>2020-04-25T06:07:29.819132+00:00</updated><author><name>利维坦</name></author><generator uri="https://igaojin.me" version="0.1">高师傅</generator><logo>http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/H22VlVkibh3stB86jje9aDBcVBU0WgKicJ5hC4XAP9lP1L7SrafCAnTo0icu3UkIBpmW5VpsJzfbQktb8RBv87Ceg/0?wx_fmt=png</logo><subtitle>乱七八糟，什么都有，微博：利维坦行星。</subtitle><entry><id>120c00141585b27a42cdbbda4a551bff</id><title>极简主义真的能让我们更快乐吗？</title><updated>2020-04-23T17:25:32+08:00</updated><content>从消费主义的角度来思考，适当减少自身欲望并没有什么错，但其理念实践也吊诡地​被商业化了。</content><link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5MzE5MTUwNQ==&amp;mid=2650503465&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4b8c6c3503ee71faef524ab2fc9be925&amp;chksm=886e7517bf19fc011ec2e833b3ecce773c81f1ecb6361105621ae730f24a6b250becf4c43d85&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd" rel="alternate"/></entry><entry><id>f4ada8d2b7595d2846f1fc841c80c439</id><title>&lt;a class="weapp_text_link" data-miniprogram-appid="d3gxM2Y3ZmExYTNkYTM1YzBl" data-miniprogram-nickname="湖畔书店" data-miniprogram-path="cGFnZXMvaG9tZS9kYXNoYm9hcmQvaW5kZXguaHRtbA==" data-miniprogram-servicetype="0" data-miniprogram-type="text" target="_blank" href="javascript:void"&gt;利维坦西文古旧书摊儿读书日优惠券限时发放，今晚24点截止，可与限时折扣同享。详见书店。&lt;/a&gt;</title><updated>2020-04-22T18:28:13+08:00</updated><content/><link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5MzE5MTUwNQ==&amp;mid=2650503463&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=dcf625c116c917d7c5e3e3c3de039537&amp;chksm=886e7519bf19fc0f9c8091a4acb9cfde303d123a79e7432a574a429d1d612345856248c45aee&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd" rel="alternate"/></entry><entry><id>94792fa802e4cdccb891f771c835827c</id><title>那些重新定义忠贞的人们</title><updated>2020-04-21T09:13:10+08:00</updated><content>我们经常把一段关系看作是独属于两人之间的互相理解。但随着人们找到重新定义爱情的方式，这种标准正受到越来越多的质疑。</content><link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5MzE5MTUwNQ==&amp;mid=2650503452&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ce92ce9ca121f5004483020d24d3b771&amp;chksm=886e7522bf19fc3493849180caca2964210e36b88c33b796a4a96d6dc69aa6b6ff4671f048e3&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd" rel="alternate"/></entry><entry><id>ceb717b212d6e38f849eb4cfc7a388e0</id><title>象头神与毛细现象的奇迹</title><updated>2020-04-19T18:07:54+08:00</updated><content>科学可以解释毛细现象——但这并不能阻止我们对这种现象怀有敬畏之心。</content><link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5MzE5MTUwNQ==&amp;mid=2650503416&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=3a4f694af24725d155515253acfc21c2&amp;chksm=886e74c6bf19fdd0c86dc4da1e9e5235d5da5468111f93d49877280d7e6d51c24320dc3a22a6&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd" rel="alternate"/></entry></feed>